3.30	Heart_of_the_Comet	Heart of the Comet	Heart of the Comet is a novel by David Brin and Gregory Benford about human space travel to Comet Halley published in 1986. Its publication coincided with the comet's 1986 approach to the Earth.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/2b/Heart_of_the_comet.jpg/200px-Heart_of_the_comet.jpg
